That's a tough one.

22
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:58,800
If only we had some way to communicate
with another part of the building.

23
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:02,199
16-year-old MVA victim.

24
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,359
He's been in and out of the hospital

25
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,879
for three weeks with internal bleeding,

26
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,939
no one can find the cause,

27
