Dad loved that.

39
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:34,140
- He was...
- Don't talk.

40
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,370
It's gonna be an hour.

41
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,459
Well, thank God you took control.

42
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:38,709
If you can't wait one hour to get your...

43
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:40,400
Kid's got hemolytic anemia.

44
00:03:40,410 --> 00:03:42,360
Kid? How old?

45
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:45,899
He must have inherited it...
He's gonna die. My condolences.

46
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:48,940
It wasn't inherited.
The problem's outside the red blood cells.

47
00:03:49,510 --> 00:03:51,699
This is impossible. A 16-year-old
doesn't get hemolytic anemia...

48
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:52,852
Give her back the file.

49
00:03:52,853 --> 00:03:55,409
You have bigger
problems to tend to, like my meds.

50
00:03:55,410 --> 00:03:58,700
Elevated indirect bilirubin,
low-serum haptoglobin...

51
00:03:58,740 --> 00:04:00,360
